If it fails, the <b>remaining</b> mean number of trials until a success is =
identical to the original mean -=20
this follows from the fact that all trials are independent.
</p><p>From this we get the formula:
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
